    <tags>dictation speech-to-text whisper local-ai wpf windows</tags>
    <summary>PrimeDictate is a fast, local speech-to-text application for Windows.</summary>
    <description>PrimeDictate is a Windows tray dictation app built with .NET and WPF. It uses local Whisper transcription for privacy-first speech-to-text, global hotkey capture, live overlay preview, and final-only text injection into the active app.</description>
